Class MapIList

  • java.lang.Object
    • wcs.java.util.MapIList

  • public class MapIList
extends java.lang.Object
    Mocked implementation of an IList useful for adding in the environment for tests You can build it easily with a List. TestElement provides a cols(String...args) method so you can set it env().setList("List", cols("a", "1", "2"), cols("b", "3", "4")
